How Do You Think Technology Affects Dating?

Have you had any experience with dating? Have you ever used dating apps? If so, what has it been like for you? If not, why not?

How do you think technology — like apps, Netflix, social media and texting — affects dating and relationships? In your opinion, does it improve or worsen romantic interactions? How so?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: technology has definitely improved the dating scene.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It also makes it much easier to find a partner for certain kinks or fetishes.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: People can become obsessed with their phone or other device to the point that you feel like your partner is ignoring you for the device.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When you are in a relationship, you need to find your love for each other and not let technology get in the way.
